item.title: Show HN：引擎 - LLM不可知论法典替代方案
item.description:
我们构建了引擎，相信可以将许多积压型软件工程任务交给远程AI代理，并在几乎没有人类参与的情况下完成异步。，一波新模型和产品浪潮吸引了很多关注的关注，以使我们的方法与我们的方法共享！ Jira, Trello, and ClickUp and also both GitHub and GitLab.- We quickly realised that configurability and workflow was important so there are lots of ways to set up and interact with Engine.- Environment set-up is a pain at the best of times so we built an agent that helps out with this.- Engine runs on all frontier LLMs, including Claude 4, which seems increasingly important with the pace of progress and competition amongst the big Labs！免费层包含Claude 4十四行诗，因此希望您能旋转引擎，让我知道它的发展！
